videos.description: Minnesota guard Rachel Banham scores 60 points, tying Cindy Brown's record for most points in an NCAA women's Division I basketball game, as the Golden Gophers top Northwestern in double overtime 112-106.
videos.headline: Minnesota's Banham ties single-game scoring mark
